{"id":612931,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paulo_Costanzo","text":"Paulo Costanzo (born September 21, 1978) is a Canadian actor. He is best known for his roles as Rubin Carver in the comedy movie \"Road Trip\" (2000), Joey Tribbiani's cousin Michael in the NBC sitcom \"Joey\" and as Evan R. Lawson in the USA Network drama series \"Royal Pains\".\nCostanzo was born in Brampton, Ontario. He is of Italian and Jewish ancestry. He is color blind.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Canadians","surface_form":"Canadian","offset":46},{"uri":"Comedy_movie","surface_form":"comedy","offset":116},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":123},{"uri":"Road_Trip_(movie)","surface_form":"Road Trip","offset":130},{"uri":"Joey_Tribbiani","surface_form":"Joey Tribbiani","offset":149},{"uri":"NBC","surface_form":"NBC","offset":188},{"uri":"Sitcom","surface_form":"sitcom","offset":192},{"uri":"Joey_(TV_series)","surface_form":"Joey","offset":200},{"uri":"USA_Network","surface_form":"USA Network","offset":235},{"uri":"Drama","surface_form":"drama","offset":247},{"uri":"Royal_Pains","surface_form":"Royal Pains","offset":261},{"uri":"Brampton%2C_Ontario","surface_form":"Brampton","offset":296},{"uri":"Ontario","surface_form":"Ontario","offset":306},{"uri":"Italians","surface_form":"Italian","offset":324},{"uri":"Jewish","surface_form":"Jewish","offset":336},{"uri":"Ancestry","surface_form":"ancestry","offset":343},{"uri":"Color_blind","surface_form":"color blind","offset":359}]}